Title: Auto Complete Textbox for VB.Net
Description: Auto Complete Textbox is a simple project to give developers a small idea on how to create a textbox which creates a popup menu with the options just below the textbox. Used Technology : VB.net and WPF.
HomeWiki:
If you want to know the approach of developing how to create an Auto Complete Textbox, then this is the project you should be looking at. Example: If you type something and you want to show the results in a small pop up beneath your textbox, the find the code here.
